{"word":"G1910 - ἐπιβαίνω - epibaínō - ep-ee-bah'-ee-no - Come","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιβαίνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epibaínō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ee-bah'-ee-no</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Come</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - போ, ஏறு"},{"paragraph":"1. to get upon, to mount"},{"paragraph":"2. to set foot in, to enter"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G939 - βάσις - básis - bas'-ece/939\">G939</a>; to <i>walk upon</i>, that is, <i>mount</i>, <i>ascend</i>, <i>embark</i>, <i>arrive:</i> - come (into), enter into, go aboard, sit upon, take ship.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}